---
import Container from "./Container.astro"

---

<div class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300" id="testimonials">
  <Container>
    <div class="mb-20 space-y-4 px-6 md:px-0">
      <h2 class="text-center text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 dark:text-white md:text-4xl">
        What our beta testers say.
      </h2>
    </div>
    <div class="md:columns-2 lg:columns-3 gap-8 space-y-8">
      <div class="aspect-auto p-8 border border-gray-100 rounded-3xl bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 dark:border-gray-700 shadow-2xl shadow-gray-600/10 dark:shadow-none">
        <div class="flex gap-4">
          <img class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full" src="./images/avatars/monke.png" alt="user avatar" width="400" height="400" loading="lazy">
          <div>
            <h6 class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-700 dark:text-white">Daniella Doe</h6>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-300">Mobile dev</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="mt-8">I had a great experience testing Skillbet. The platform is user-friendly and the variety of games available is impressive. I found it easy to navigate and the overall design is visually appealing. The support team was quick to help when I encountered any issues. Highly recommended!</p>
      </div>
      <div class="aspect-auto p-8 border border-gray-100 rounded-3xl bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 dark:border-gray-700 shadow-2xl shadow-gray-600/10 dark:shadow-none">
        <div class="flex gap-4">
          <img class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full" src="./images/avatars/monkee.png" alt="user avatar" width="200" height="200" loading="lazy">
          <div>
            <h6 class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-700 dark:text-white">Jane doe</h6>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-300">Marketing</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="mt-8"> Skillbet has an excellent selection of games that cater to different skill levels. The platform is easy to use and provides a seamless experience. I was particularly impressed with the customer support, who were prompt and efficient in resolving any queries I had. I'm excited to see what new games will be added in the future!</p>
      </div>
      <div class="aspect-auto p-8 border border-gray-100 rounded-3xl bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 dark:border-gray-700 shadow-2xl shadow-gray-600/10 dark:shadow-none">
        <div class="flex gap-4">
          <img class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full" src="./images/avatars/monkeee.png" alt="user avatar" width="200" height="200" loading="lazy">
          <div>
            <h6 class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-700 dark:text-white">Yanick Doe</h6>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-300">Developer</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="mt-8">I'm impressed with the overall functionality of Skillbet. The platform is well-designed and provides a smooth gaming experience. The variety of games is great, and I enjoyed trying them all out. I appreciate the responsiveness of the support team, who were always ready to help with any concerns. Keep up the good work!</p>
      </div>
      <div class="aspect-auto p-8 border border-gray-100 rounded-3xl bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 dark:border-gray-700 shadow-2xl shadow-gray-600/10 dark:shadow-none">
        <div class="flex gap-4">
          <img class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full" src="./images/avatars/defi.png" alt="user avatar" width="200" height="200" loading="lazy">
          <div>
            <h6 class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-700 dark:text-white">Defi Land</h6>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-300">Mobile dev</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="mt-8">The second game I tested on Skillbet was enjoyable and challenging. The interface is clean and easy to use, and I had no issues navigating through the platform. The customer support team was always on hand to help when needed. I'm looking forward to exploring more games on the platform!</p>
      </div>
      <div class="aspect-auto p-8 border border-gray-100 rounded-3xl bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 dark:border-gray-700 shadow-2xl shadow-gray-600/10 dark:shadow-none">
