            <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-300">Manager</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="mt-8"> Skillbet continues to impress with its wide range of games and user-friendly interface. Game 2 provided a different challenge, and I enjoyed playing it just as much as the first game. The support team has been consistently responsive and helpful. I can't wait to see how the platform evolves!</p>
      </div>
      <div class="aspect-auto p-8 border border-gray-100 rounded-3xl bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 dark:border-gray-700 shadow-2xl shadow-gray-600/10 dark:shadow-none">
        <div class="flex gap-4">
          <img class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full" src="./images/avatars/evio.png" alt="user avatar" width="400" height="400" loading="lazy">
          <div>
            <h6 class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-700 dark:text-white">Ev.io</h6>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-300">Mobile dev</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="mt-8">I had a blast playing Game 2 on Skillbet! The platform is easy to navigate, and I found the game both engaging and challenging. The customer support team was always ready to help when I needed assistance. I'm excited to continue testing more games on Skillbet!

</p>
